{"tid":1867951,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"事實證明罷工有效","createTime":"2020-02-07T10:51:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-07T11:07:41.000Z","uid":62935,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"090b2e28f6778ae69492d5348c6766e2fe940c4f","tid":1867951,"uid":62935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:51:14.000Z","msg":"連登仔唔係以為一罷工林鄭就會仆出來跪低斟茶叩頭認錯呀？<br />\n<br />\n羸一半都係羸"},{"pid":"eeff240e3952a233e0d2efcfb526d9930683f82e","tid":1867951,"uid":107577,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:52:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>即使醫護唔繼續罷<br />\n佢地都係成功！<br />\n<br />\n唔罷 唔等於 失敗<br />\n如果一陣投票結果係唔繼續<br />\n都唔可以 spin 到係失敗<br />\n記住,大家要既係士氣<br />\n連 HA 工會都自認失敗，咁就咬住食。<br />\n重申,唔繼續罷 不等於 失敗<br />\n<br />\n係政府同 HA 不聽訴求 專制橫蠻<br />\n<br />\n記者會同會員大會做個小總結<br />\n講大家成功做咗 d 咩<br />\n增加士氣<br />\n唔好淨係 FOCUS 政府冇做 d 咩先。<br />\neg<br />\n- 有幾多人參加咗工會<br />\n- 呢幾日有幾多人罷工<br />\n- 令到政府由唔封關，到局部封關（但仍唔足夠），都係醫護罷工所 做到既其中一個成果<br />\n- 令大家長遠關注同監察 HA 資源問題，對 HA, 醫護，病人都係好事<br />\n</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gLrYQB4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgLrYQB4.jpg&h=f72ededb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6SwmOoL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6SwmOoL.png&h=96bc9ec5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"870ffbd708f9b847b1c55bf6cd27f643f717f17e","tid":1867951,"uid":36901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:54:42.000Z","msg":"起碼逼到條撚樣封左部份關<br />\n雖然已經走晒落黎<br />\n已經社區爆發緊<br />\n但全世界包括藍屍都睇到係七婆做成"},{"pid":"dbe5c7556bc9a0138815b864ba86a898b93dd24a","tid":1867951,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:56:49.000Z","msg":"醫護後續行動！變相港人優先，對非粵語病人執行超審慎政策<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1848237/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1848237/page/1</a>"},{"pid